      <title>假化肥可能导致肯尼亚农业部长下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/fake-fertilizer-may-lead-to-kenyan-agriculture-minister-s-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在政府机构通过补贴计划分发假化肥后，肯尼亚立法者要求解雇该国农业部长，这是威廉·鲁托总统政府遭受的最新丑闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/fake-fertilizer-may-lead-to-kenyan-agriculture-minister-s-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 13:33:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯·格里芬资助反对麦卡锡罢免背后的立法者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Citadel 的肯·格里芬 (Ken Griffin) 正在出资推动击败前众议院议长凯文·麦卡锡 (Kevin McCarthy) 下台的保守派之一，以重塑分裂严重的共和党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/ken-griffin-funds-push-against-lawmaker-behind-mccarthy-ouster</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士邀请160多个国家参加乌克兰会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/switzerland-invites-more-than-160-states-to-ukraine-conference</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士已邀请 160 多个国家参加计划中的乌克兰和平蓝图会议，但嘉宾名单中不包括俄罗斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/switzerland-invites-more-than-160-states-to-ukraine-conference</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:57:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟提供10亿欧元帮助黎巴嫩管理叙利亚难民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/eu-offers-1-billion-to-help-lebanon-manage-syrian-refugees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟委员会主席乌苏拉·冯德莱恩周四宣布，欧盟将向黎巴嫩提供为期三年的 10 亿欧元（10.7 亿美元）一揽子计划，主要用于帮助管理该国的难民人口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/eu-offers-1-billion-to-help-lebanon-manage-syrian-refugees</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 11:35:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪在南部主要邦的盟友被指控拍摄性犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/modi-s-ally-in-key-southern-state-accused-of-filming-sex-crimes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度南部重要的卡纳塔克邦因与总理纳伦德拉·莫迪结盟的地区政党的一名议员性虐待多名妇女并离开该国以避免面临指控的指控而受到震动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/modi-s-ally-in-key-southern-state-accused-of-filming-sex-crimes</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:54:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏格兰民族党的约翰·斯温尼将在优素福离开后继续担任领导职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/scottish-national-party-s-john-swinney-to-stand-for-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[约翰·斯温尼 (John Swinney) 表示，在苏格兰执政党苏格兰民族党 (Scottish National Party) 首席部长宣布辞职后，他计划参加接替胡姆扎·优素福 (Humza Yousaf) 领导人的竞选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/scottish-national-party-s-john-swinney-to-stand-for-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 10:11:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方在驱散令后拆除了加州大学洛杉矶分校的抗议营地</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前一天晚上与反抗议者发生暴力事件后，身着防暴装备的警察拆除了亲巴勒斯坦抗议者在洛杉矶加州大学搭建的路障和帐篷。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/tensions-high-at-ucla-as-protesters-ordered-to-disperse</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:45:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>必和必拓首席执行官飞往南非推动 390 亿美元收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司已向南非部署了包括首席执行官在内的高级团队，这家全球最大的矿业公司正在加大努力争取政府官员、监管机构和当地股东的支持，所有这些人都可能会决定其拟议合作的结果与竞争对手英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 合作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/bhp-woos-south-africa-in-pursuit-of-39-billion-anglo-takeover</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 08:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾水炮事件后召见中国特使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/philippines-summons-china-envoy-after-water-cannon-incident</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾周四召见中国驻马尼拉特使，抗议中国在有争议的南海对其船只使用高压水枪，促使北京指责马尼拉侵犯其领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-02/philippines-summons-china-envoy-after-water-cannon-incident</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 May 2024 04:17:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
